<section class="card">
  <div class="card-body">


    <h1 class="card-title">
      &#123;&#123;froala-content&#125;&#125;
      <small class="text-muted">Component</small>
    </h1>
    <hr />


    <p class="lead">
      According to the <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor/docs/overview#frontend" target="_blank">Froala Editor documentation</a>, content created from the editor should be contained within an element with the <code class="bg-light text-dark">.fr-view</code> class. This is simply a component that applies the class.
    </p>


    <div class="row small-gutters">
      <div class="col-sm-6">


        <h5>Handlebars Template</h5>
        <pre class="bg-light border rounded p-2 text-dark">&#123;&#123;#froala-content&#125;&#125;
  &#123;&#123;someFroalaContent&#125;&#125;
&#123;&#123;/froala-content&#125;&#125;</pre>


      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">


        <h5>Generates HTML</h5>
        <pre class="bg-light border rounded p-2 text-dark">&lt;div class="fr-view"&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Some Froala Editor content...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre>


      </div>
    </div>


  </div>{{!-- .card-body --}}
</section>{{!-- .card --}}




<section class="card">
  <div class="card-body">


    <h2 class="card-title">
      Usages
    </h2>


    <p class="lead">
      This component is very basic, mainly just a wrapper for the class.
      However, you can use it inline (specifying the attribute or using <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v3.0.0/components/passing-properties-to-a-component/#toc_positional-params" target="_blank">positional params</a>) or as a block.
      Any way will produce the same result.
    </p>


    <div class="row small-gutters">
      <div class="col-sm-6">


        <h5>Inline</h5>
          <pre class="bg-light border rounded p-2 text-dark">&#123;&#123;froala-content content=someFroalaContent&#125;&#125;</pre>
          <pre class="bg-light border rounded p-2 text-dark">&#123;&#123;froala-content someFroalaContent&#125;&#125;</pre>


      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6">


        <h5>Block</h5>
          <pre class="bg-light border rounded p-2 text-dark">&#123;&#123;#froala-content&#125;&#125;
  &#123;&#123;someFroalaContent&#125;&#125;
&#123;&#123;/froala-content&#125;&#125;</pre>


      </div>
    </div>


    <p>
      Note: You can also change the element type by adjusting the <a href="https://guides.emberjs.com/v3.0.0/components/customizing-a-components-element/#toc_customizing-the-element" target="_blank">Ember Components tagName property</a>. Ex: <code class="bg-light text-dark">&#123;&#123;froala-content tagName="section"&#125;&#125;</code>
    </p>


  </div>{{!-- .card-body --}}
</section>{{!-- .card --}}
